# 3. あの日の夜

Mafuyu's Father: I see. I'm glad to hear that you're doing well.
Mafuyu's Father: Has your computer been working properly?
Mafuyu: Yes, everything I had saved was still there...
Mafuyu: Thank you...
Mafuyu's Father: I see...
Mafuyu's Father: *Nod* That's good to hear.
Mafuyu's Father: ...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: Um, Dad...?
Mafuyu's Father: Oh, uhh... Sorry... I was just thinking about everything and...
Mafuyu: About everything...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: I'm really sorry...
Mafuyu's Father: No, you don't need to apologize. You've done nothing wrong, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu: But...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu's Father: You're so kind, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu's Father: In that case, would you mind if I asked you a question...?
Mafuyu: Okay, sure...
Mafuyu's Father: It's about...what you and your mother talked about that night.
Mafuyu: ...!
Mafuyu's Father: Your mother has told me her side of the story in terms of what occurred...
Mafuyu's Father: But there's no way for me to uncover the truth without a corroborating statement.
Mafuyu's Father: I know this is a difficult matter for you to discuss, but if you can tell me what happened that night...
Mafuyu: What happened that night...
Mafuyu: That night... That night...
Mafuyu: I told Mom...
Mafuyu: ...!
Kanade: Mafuyu...!
Mafuyu's Father: A-Are you okay?!
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: (Why...?)
Mafuyu: (I need to tell him...)
Mafuyu: (But I...)
Mafuyu: I'm sorry...
Mafuyu: I'm really sorry...
Mafuyu's Father: No, it's okay... Thank you for trying.
Mafuyu's Father: I'm sorry if I asked too much of you.
Mafuyu's Father: You don't have to answer.
Mafuyu: ...
Kanade: How do you feel, Mafuyu?
Mafuyu: *Nod* A little better...
Mafuyu: Where's my dad?
Kanade: He looked very concerned, but he left after saying that we should let you rest today.
Mafuyu: Really?
Kanade: But you still look a little pale, so you really should try to rest today...
Mafuyu: You're right...
Mafuyu: I'm sorry.
Kanade: There's no need for you to apologize, Mafuyu.
Kanade: Just try to rest for now. I'll tell the others about what's going on.
Mafuyu: Okay.
Mafuyu: I want to spend more time finding a dream that suits me better...
Mafuyu's Mother: ...
Mafuyu's Mother: I see. Now I understand, Mafuyu.
Mafuyu: Mom...
Mafuyu's Mother: How can you say such a thing...?
Mafuyu's Mother: How did things end up like this...?
Mafuyu: Huh...?
Mafuyu's Mother: Mafuyu, you spent so much time studying and working so hard to become a doctor...
Mafuyu: ...!
Mafuyu: I'm really sorry, Mom...
Mafuyu: But I...
???: I agree.
Mafuyu: What...?
Mafuyu's Father: I agree with your mother. You should be striving to become a doctor.
Mafuyu's Father: Honestly, how did things end up like this...?
Mafuyu's Father: I'm so disappointed.
Mafuyu: ...!!!
Mafuyu: Huff... Huff...
Mafuyu: It was a dream...?
???: <Mafuyu?>
Mafuyu: Huh...?
